<h1> netCFD: a Demonstration of Ninf and femFlow </h1>

This is a GUI interface to CFD simulation.<br>
The applet connects with a Ninf Server on pdplab.trc.rwcp.or.jp.<br>
<p>
<ul>
<li>Click "Load" Button to select the mesh file in the server. <br>
<li> Chick "Start" Button to start a simulation on the loaded mesh data.
<li> You may change the view by selecting the display modes:
<ul> 
<li> Vector, the direction of flow
<li> Element, showing the value by painted colors.
<li> Mesh, viewing mesh data
</ul>
<li> You may also select the values for the color:
<ul> 
<li> Pressure
<li> Velocity
<li> Temperature
</ul>
</ul>
<hr>
<applet codebase="showflow.java" code="ShowFlow.class" width=700 height=700>
<param name=host value= "pdplab.trc.rwcp.or.jp">
<param name=port value= "3000"> 
</applet>

</body>
